            Плащания в текущ месец: @ViewBag.bagUpcomingPaymentsInTheCurrentMonth
        </p>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <p class="border-left border-right border-top font-weight-bold p-4">
            Общо клиенти: @ViewBag.CountOfClients
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <p class="border-left border-right border-top font-weight-bold p-4">
            Детски градини: @ViewBag.bagCountOfKindergartens
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <p class="border-left border-right border-top font-weight-bold p-4">
            Училища: @ViewBag.bagCountOfSchools
